==Vietnamese==
===Etymology===
Contratry to some proposals (such as Ishihara (2014)<ref>Ishihara, Yoshihito 石原, 嘉人 (2014), [https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1050855676747884928 ベトナム語話者に対する漢字語彙の指導について (Native Speakers of Vietnamese and the Acquisition of Japanese KANJI Compounds)]</ref>), this term is unrelated to {{ltc-l|請|id=2}}, which contains both an unmatching velar coda and an unmatching tone.
===Pronunciation===
{{vi-pron}}
===Verb===
{{vi-verb|[[嗔]], [[吀]]}}
# to [[ask]] for; to [[beg]] for; to [[request]]
#:{{uxi|vi|'''xin''' tiền|to ask for an allowance; to beg for money; to request a budget}}
#:{{ux|vi|{{lb|vi|honorific}} '''Xin''' anh vui lòng cởi giày trước khi vào nhà ạ.|Please take off your shoes before coming in.|lit=I beg you to take off your shoes before entering my house.}}
# {{lb|vi|honorific|humble}} to [[humbly]] ask to do something
#:{{ux|vi|'''Xin''' chân thành cảm ơn mọi người đã tụ họp đông đủ tại đây.|I'd like to thank everyone for attending this meeting, with no one being absent.}}
